animeDescription: Shoot for the stars! I'm going to be the country's number one alchemist!When young girl Sarasa graduated from the Royal Alchemist Academy, her teacher gifted her a house for her to set up shop. Aiming to become a masterclass alchemist, she gathers materials herself, experiments and operates a business. In her very own atelier, Sarasa indulges in a slow and relaxed alchemist life! (Source: Kadokawa, edited)
